<font face="Tahoma">د ۲۰۲۱ ز کال په جولای میاشت کې تاجیکستان د روسیې په مشرۍ د ټولیز امنیت د پیمان د پخواني شوروي اتحاد له غړو هېوادونو نه له ګاونډي افغانستان نه دغه هېواد ته د را ولاړېدونکو امنیتي ګواښونو اړوند مرسته وغوښته. دغه امنیتي ګواښونه، له افغانستان نه د متحده ایالاتو او بریتانوي ځواکونو له وتلو رامنځته شوي وو، چې له امله یې ۱۰۰۰ کسه افغان ملکي وګړي او دولتي مامورین وروسته له هغه چې طالب یاغیانو، د افغانستان په ډېرو برخو کنټرول ترلاسه <ref>{{cite news|title=Tajikistan asks Russia-led bloc for help on Afghan border|url=https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/russia-says-afghan-situation-can-swiftly-worsen-pledges-help-if-needed-2021-07-07/|work=Reuters|date=7 July 2021}}</ref>کړ، ګاونډي تاجیکستان ته وتښتېدل.<ref>{{Cite web|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|title=Press freedom in Tajikistan: Going from bad to worse {{!}} DW {{!}} 05.06.2020|url=https://www.dw.com/en/press-freedom-in-tajikistan-going-from-bad-to-worse/a-53697778|access-date=2021-01-05|website=DW.COM|language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://iwpr.net/report-news/tajik-government%E2%80%99s-fury-over-conflict-reporting|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140926061259/http://iwpr.net/report-news/tajik-government%E2%80%99s-fury-over-conflict-reporting|url-status=dead|archive-date=26 September 2014|title=Tajik Government's Fury Over Conflict Reporting|publisher=Iwpr.net|date=22 October 2010|access-date=14 January 2011}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Global democracy has another bad year|work=The Economist|url=https://www.economist.com/graphic-detail/2020/01/22/global-democracy-has-another-bad-year|access-date=2020-07-27|issn=0013-0613}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Which Countries Are For or Against China's Xinjiang Policies?|url=https://thediplomat.com/2019/07/which-countries-are-for-or-against-chinas-xinjiang-policies/|work=[[The Diplomat]]|date=15 July 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/10/12/tajikistan-leader-rakhmon-wins-election-with-over-90-p